</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Marina del Rey" /><category term="Aerial" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking north at the Marina del Rey harbor entrance after takeoff from LAX airport. In the distance are Venice, Santa Monica, and the Santa Monica mountains. マリナ・デル・レイ ロサンゼルス国際空港離陸後に、マリナ・デル・レイ港の入り口を北に眺める。遠くに見えるのはベニス、サンタモニカ、サンタモニカの山々。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09407_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09407_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Beautiful Beach</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250907/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Beautiful Beach" /><published>2025-09-07T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-09-07T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250907/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
