</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Torrance" /><category term="Art" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Cherry tomatoes in the sun, at the Torrance Farmers Market. ファーマーズマーケット 太陽の下のチェリートマト、トーランス・ファーマーズマーケットにて。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09396_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09396_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Setting Sun</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250902/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Setting Sun" /><published>2025-09-02T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-09-02T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa-sun</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250902/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
