</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Lifeguard Towers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[I like seeing the sun get distorted by the atmosphere at the horizon. Taken in north Hermosa Beach. In the distance is an oil tanker at the Chevron El Segundo refinery. 夕日 大気によって地平線で歪む太陽を見るのが好きだ。北ハーモサビーチで撮影。遠くにはシェブロン・エルセグンド製油所に停泊するタンカーが見える。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09374_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09374_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Orange &amp;amp; Purple Mountains</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250831/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Orange &amp;amp; Purple Mountains" /><published>2025-08-31T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-31T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/purple-mountains</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250831/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
