</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Mountains" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Dusk" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking north at Topanga and Malibu, from across the Santa Monica Bay in Palos Verdes. オレンジと紫の山々 パロスバーデスからサンタモニカ湾を隔てて、トパンガとマリブ方面を北方向に見渡す景色。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R09351-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R09351-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">TK Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250830/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="TK Sunset" /><published>2025-08-30T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-08-30T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/TK-sunset</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250830/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
